<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Date::set() returns a string or integer instead of the Zend_Date Object, preventing the use of method chaining. Setters, as a general rule, should return the method's object instead of the value that you just set.</p>

